226
00:11:57,400 --> 00:12:00,500
Scott: Well, not zero to do with each other, but not that much.

227
00:12:01,222 --> 00:12:08,040
Scott: There was Macross, legendary, amazing robot show, which was Super Dimension Fortress Macross.

228
00:12:08,580 --> 00:12:15,500
Scott: Then there was the Southern Cross show, and Southern Cross was actually called Super Dimension Century Southern Cross.

229
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:20,500
Scott: So there was some relation with the Super Dimension thing, but the shows had nothing to do with each other.

230
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:23,560
Scott: They were like different characters, different plots.

231
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:25,040
