246
00:13:20,031 --> 00:13:21,578
Scott: It was basically a travesty.

247
00:13:22,922 --> 00:13:24,611
Scott: But it did expose the U.S.

248
00:13:24,711 --> 00:13:26,240
Scott: audience to Macross at least.

249
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:29,800
Rym: It was extremely popular in America and in Europe.

250
00:13:30,060 --> 00:13:33,969
Scott: There were some positive side effects, and there were arguments to be made.

251
00:13:33,989 --> 00:13:44,520
