00:18:41,740 --> 00:18:47,233
Rym: Harmony gold, I think can release the Robotech movie in Japan.

324
00:18:47,313 --> 00:18:50,060
Rym: now, I guess there's an upcoming Robotech movie that we haven't talked about yet.

325
00:18:50,781 --> 00:18:50,981
Scott: Yup.

326
00:18:51,422 --> 00:19:03,500
Scott: So yeah, so what's happened is now after these like renewals that sort of just sort of kept a sort of steady state for a while, all the parties involved got together and just made some sort of agreement that we only know part of.

327
00:19:04,381 --> 00:19:06,845
Scott: And it's a good news, bad news, right?

